data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis nestled in a serene gated community! Ideal location close to Ballantyne, Pineville and Fort Mill This exquisite property boasts luxury and comfort, offering the epitome of modern living on a sprawling lot.  Step into this stunning home and immerse yourself in the beauty of open living. The sliders open to the screened in  porch that overlooks serene views of the wooded backyard and in ground pool, wonderful for lounging and entertaining. This home offers the perfect balance of indoor-outdoor living. Entertainment is taken to another level in this sizable kitchen with a large center island, custom cabinetry, gas cooktop, and coffee/beverage bar. Primary BR on main level and overlooks views of the backyard. 2 additional BR on main level, one of which could be an office. Upstairs you will find 2 huge BR and a theater room great for enjoying your favorite films. Schedule a viewing today and experience the blend of elegance and functionality in your home!
